# NEHotspotHelperConfidence.none

**Case**

The helper is unable to handle the network.

## Declaration

```swift
case none
```

## Confidence Levels

- **NEHotspotHelperConfidence.high**: The helper has high confidence in being able to handle the network.
- **NEHotspotHelperConfidence.low**: The helper has some confidence in being able to handle the network.
